      <title>en</title>
      <link>https://vishvAsa.github.io/rAmAnujIyam/kAvyam/drAviDam/4k-divya-prabandha/sarva-prastutiH/18_tiruvAsiriyam_nammALHvar_2578-2584/sArathi-dAsaH/en/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>https://vishvAsa.github.io/rAmAnujIyam/kAvyam/drAviDam/4k-divya-prabandha/sarva-prastutiH/18_tiruvAsiriyam_nammALHvar_2578-2584/sArathi-dAsaH/en/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;Source: &lt;a href=&#34;https://divyaprabandham.koyil.org/index.php/2017/06/thiruvasiriyam/&#34;&gt;TW&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;SrI: SrImathE SatakOpAya nama: SrImathE rAmAnujAya nama: SrImath varavaramunayE nama:&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://divyaprabandham.koyil.org/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/paramapadhanathan.jpg&#34;&gt;&lt;figure class=&#34;&#34;&gt;&#xA;&#xA;    &lt;a href=&#34;https://divyaprabandham.koyil.org/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/paramapadhanathan.jpg&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;&#xA;        &lt;img src=&#34;https://divyaprabandham.koyil.org/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/paramapadhanathan.jpg&#34; alt=&#34;&#34; title=&#34;&#34;&gt;&#xA;    &lt;/a&gt;&#xA;&#xA;    &#xA;&#xA;&lt;/figure&gt;&#xA;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;http://acharyas.koyil.org/index.php/sriman-narayanan/&#34;&gt;SrIman nArAyaNan&lt;/a&gt; in paramapadham&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://divyaprabandham.koyil.org/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/Nammalwar-alwai-thirthavari.jpg&#34;&gt;&lt;figure class=&#34;&#34;&gt;&#xA;&#xA;    &lt;a href=&#34;https://divyaprabandham.koyil.org/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/Nammalwar-alwai-thirthavari.jpg&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;&#xA;        &lt;img src=&#34;https://divyaprabandham.koyil.org/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/Nammalwar-alwai-thirthavari.jpg&#34; alt=&#34;&#34; title=&#34;&#34;&gt;&#xA;    &lt;/a&gt;&#xA;&#xA;    &#xA;&#xA;&lt;/figure&gt;&#xA;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;http://acharyas.koyil.org/index.php/nammazhwar/&#34;&gt;nammAzhwAr&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;e-book – &lt;a href=&#34;https://1drv.ms/b/s!AiNzc-LF3uwyhgtrMYxYW-9aza70&#34;&gt;https://1drv.ms/b/s!AiNzc-LF3uwyhgtrMYxYW-9aza70&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://divyaprabandham.koyil.org/index.php/2019/03/thiruvasiriyam-audio/&#34;&gt;Audio&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;All the &lt;a href=&#34;http://acharyas.koyil.org/index.php/azhwars/&#34;&gt;AzhwArs&lt;/a&gt; are &lt;em&gt;‘mayarvaRa madhinalam aruLappeRRavar’&lt;/em&gt;, i.e. they are bestowed with&lt;br&gt;&#xA;unblemished knowledge and devotion by &lt;a href=&#34;https://granthams.koyil.org/2013/03/12/thathva-thrayam-iswara-who-is-god/&#34;&gt;bhagavAn&lt;/a&gt; himself, through his nirhEthuka katAksha&lt;br&gt;&#xA;(unconditional graceful glance).Of them nammAzhwAr is called prapanna jana kUtastha&lt;br&gt;&#xA;(leader of surrendered devotees). He has written four prabandhams namely,&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;thiruviruththam&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;thiruvAsiriyam&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;periya thiruvandhAdhi and&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;thiruvAimozhi&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;These four prabandhams are considered to be equivalent to four vEdhams in thamizh&lt;br&gt;&#xA;language. Of them thiruvAsiriyam is the yajur vEdham equiavalent. This is the 6th prabandham&lt;br&gt;&#xA;in the iyaRpA.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>ta</title>
      <link>https://vishvAsa.github.io/rAmAnujIyam/kAvyam/drAviDam/4k-divya-prabandha/sarva-prastutiH/18_tiruvAsiriyam_nammALHvar_2578-2584/sArathi-dAsaH/ta/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>https://vishvAsa.github.io/rAmAnujIyam/kAvyam/drAviDam/4k-divya-prabandha/sarva-prastutiH/18_tiruvAsiriyam_nammALHvar_2578-2584/sArathi-dAsaH/ta/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;Source: &lt;a href=&#34;https://divyaprabandham.koyil.org/index.php/2020/05/thiruvasiriyam-tamil-simple/&#34;&gt;TW&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;श्री: श्रीमदे सडगोबाय नम: श्रीमदे रामानुजाय नम: श्रीमत् वरवरमुनये नम:&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://divyaprabandham.koyil.org/index.php/iyarpa/&#34;&gt;इयऱ्पा&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;figure class=&#34;&#34;&gt;&#xA;&#xA;    &lt;a href=&#34;https://divyaprabandham.koyil.org/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/paramapadhanathan.jpg&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;&#xA;        &lt;img src=&#34;https://divyaprabandham.koyil.org/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/paramapadhanathan.jpg&#34; alt=&#34;&#34; title=&#34;&#34;&gt;&#xA;    &lt;/a&gt;&#xA;&#xA;    &#xA;&#xA;&lt;/figure&gt;&#xA;&lt;figure class=&#34;&#34;&gt;&#xA;&#xA;    &lt;a href=&#34;https://divyaprabandham.koyil.org/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/Nammalwar-alwai-thirthavari.jpg&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;&#xA;        &lt;img src=&#34;https://divyaprabandham.koyil.org/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/Nammalwar-alwai-thirthavari.jpg&#34; alt=&#34;&#34; title=&#34;&#34;&gt;&#xA;    &lt;/a&gt;&#xA;&#xA;    &#xA;&#xA;&lt;/figure&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;श्रीमन्नारायणऩाल् मयर्वऱ मदिनलम् अरुळप्पॆऱ्ऱवर्गळ् आऴ्वार्गळ् ऎऩ्ऱु कॊण्डाडप्पडुगिऱार्गळ्। अवर्गळुळ् तलैवराऩ नम्माऴ्वार् तिरुविरुत्तम्, तिरुवासिरियम्, पॆरिय तिरुवन्दादि, तिरुवाय्मॊऴि ऎऩ्ऱु नाऩ्गु अऱ्पुद प्रबन्दङ्गळै अरुळियुळ्ळार्।&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;अवऱ्ऱुळ् तिरुविरुत्तत्तिल्, सर्वेच्वरऩुडैय स्वरूब, रूब, कुण, विबूदिगळै ऎल्लाम् अवऩ् काट्टिक्कॊडुक्कक् कण्ड आऴ्वार्, अवऩ् परमबदत्तिल् नित्यसूरिगळुडऩुम् मुक्तर्गळुडऩुम् आऩन्दमाग इरुप्पदै निऩैत्तु, इन्द संसारत्तिल् उळ्ळवर्गळ् अदऱ्कुत् तगुदि पॆऱ्ऱिरुन्दुम् अदै इऴन्दिरुप्पदै निऩैत्तु, अप्पडि इऴन्दिरुप्पवर्गळिल् ताऩुम् ऒरुवर् ऎऩ्ऱु उणर्न्दु, इदऱ्कुक् कारणम् इव्वुलगिल् इन्द तेहत्तुडऩ् इरुप्पदे ऎऩ्ऱु पार्त्तु वरुन्दुगिऱार्।, अदैक् कऴित्तुक् कॊळ्ळ तऩ्ऩिडत्तिल् ऎन्द सक्तियुम्, तगुदियुम् इल्लै ऎऩ्बदै उणर्न्दु ऎम्बॆरुमाऩिडत्तिले “इव्वुलगिल् नाऩ् इरुक्कुम् इरुप्पै अऱुत्तरुळ वेण्डुम्” ऎऩ्ऱु प्रार्त्तित्तार्।&lt;/p&gt;</description>
